lfs-pkmg
lfs package manager

Simple package management solution for LFS / BLFS https://www.linuxfromscratch.org/

--------------------------------------------------------------------
QUICK START:
1) run make
2) accept defaults, enter alternate browser if desired for viewing docs
--------------------------------------------------------------------


lfs-pkmg (pronounced 'pacmag')(lpm for short) does the following:

Build
Automated build of lfs and blfs packages. Generates a portable package archive that can be installed, removed, and upgraded on any compatible system.

Install
Install package archive generated during the build phase.

Remove
Remove package files associated with an installed package archive.

Upgrade
Upgrade package files associated with an installed package archive.
